description: Should return query for getting records with end parameter

expectedResult.query: SELECT id, time, z00_data record FROM (SELECT z13_rec_key id, z13_upd_time_stamp time FROM foo00.z13 s1 WHERE s1.z13_rec_key > :cursor AND s1.z13_rec_key <= 999999998 AND s1.z13_upd_time_stamp <= :endTime  ORDER BY s1.z13_rec_key FETCH NEXT 101 ROWS ONLY) JOIN foo00.z00 ON id = z00_doc_number
